nt":"Writing","name":"Atsushi Ohkubo","original_name":"大久保篤","popularity":0.6944,"profile_path":null,"credit_id":"641b2817142ef100837eeb54","department":"Writing","job":"Comic Book"}],"id":88046}},"person_1972402_translations":{"at":1774718568332,"data":{"id":1972402,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Kana Ichinose (市ノ瀬 加那, December 20) is a Japanese voice actress from Hokkaido. She is affiliated with Sigma Seven. She played her first main role in 2018 as Ichigo in the anime series Darling in the Franxx.","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"이치노세 카나","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"市之瀨加那是日本的女性聲優。出身於北海道，所屬公司為 Sigma Seven。","name":"市之瀨加那","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"市ノ瀬加那","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"市之濑加那（日语：市ノ瀬 加那／いちのせ かな Ichinose Kana，1996年12月20日—）是日本的女性声优、电视艺人。Sigma Seven所属。北海道出身。\n\n小时候就喜欢动画，但真正热爱起来是在初中一、二年级的时候，当时迷上了《网球王子》。成为声优的契机是从热爱动画后开始考虑投身于与动画相关的职业，并在思考自己的未来时，开始参加与此相关的学校的开放日活动，希望找到相关职业的出路。\n\n在其中一次参加声优课程的开放日活动中，她在自我介绍时用自己的真实声音回答，然后被讲师问到“那是你的自然声音吗？”，她回答说“是的”，讲师说：“我觉得你非常适合这个职业”，于是开始强烈地考虑成为一名声优。\n\n札幌放送艺术专门学校出身。2016年4月加入Sigma Seven事务所。2018年1月在《DARLING in the FRANXX》中为莓配音，首次声演主要角色。2021年3月获得第15回声优奖新人女优赏。2021年11月1日，从所属事务所Sigma Seven e升格至Sigma Seven。2023年3月获得第18回声优奖主演声优赏。\n\n爱好是独自旅行、观察天空、看电影。中小学生时代爱好篮球，现在仍是特长。资格有危险物处理者丙级、演示制作检定3级、日语文字处理检定3级、信息处理技能检定2级、个人电脑速度认定3级。","name":"市之濑加那","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"ES","iso_639_1":"es","name":"Español","english_name":"Spanish","data":{"biography":"Kana Ichinose (市ノ瀬 加那, 20 de diciembre) es una actriz de voz japonesa de Hokkaido. Está afiliada a Sigma Seven. Desempeñó su primer papel principal en el 2018 como Ichigo en la serie de anime Darling in the Franxx.","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"คานะ อิจิโนเซะ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kana Ičinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кана Ічіносе","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Кана Итиносэ","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"市之瀨加那是日本的女性聲優。出身於北海道，所屬公司為 Sigma Seven。","name":"市之瀨加那","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Kana Ichinose (市ノ瀬 加那) est une doubleuse japonaise originaire de Obihiro. Elle a joué son premier rôle principal en 2018 dans le rôle d'Ichigo dans la série animée Darling in the Franxx.","name":"Kana Ichinose","primary":false}}]}},"person_77287_translations":{"at":1774718577774,"data":{"id":77287,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Anne Reid, MBE is an English stage, film and television actress, known for her roles as Valerie Barlow in the soap opera Coronation Street; Jean in the sitcom dinnerladies; and her BAFTA-nominated role as Celia Dawson in Last Tango in Halifax.","name":"Anne Reid","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"安妮·里德（Anne Reid），MBE是一位英国舞台、电影和电视女演员，因在肥皂剧《加冕街》中饰演瓦莱丽·巴洛（Valerie Barlow）而闻名;情景喜剧《晚宴女士》中的吉恩;以及她在哈利法克斯的《最后的探戈》中饰演西莉亚·道森（Celia Dawson）的英国电影学院奖提名角色。","name":"安妮·里德","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Энн Рейд","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"安妮·里德（Anne Reid），MBE 是一位英國舞台、電影和電視女演員，因在肥皂劇《加冕街》中飾演瓦萊麗·巴洛（Valerie Barlow）而聞名; 情景喜劇《晚宴女士》中的吉恩; 以及她在哈利法克斯的《最後的探戈》中飾演西莉亞·道森（Celia Dawson）的英國電影學院獎提名角色。","name":"安妮·里德","primary":false}}]}},"person_1544092_translations":{"at":1774718578542,"data":{"id":1544092,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Park Ji-min (박지민; born October 13, 1995), known mononymously as Jimin (지민), is a South Korean singer, songwriter, record producer and dancer under BigHit Music. He is a member of the boy group BTS.\n\nJimin has released three solo tracks under BTS' name—\"Lie\" in 2016, \"Serendipity\" in 2017, and \"Filter\" in 2020—all of which have charted on South Korea's Gaon Digital Chart. He released two self-composed digital singles, \"Promise\" in 2018 and \"Christmas Love\" in 2020. He also recorded the duet \"With You\" with Ha Sung-woon for the soundtrack for the TvN drama Our Blues in 2022. Jimin released his debut solo album, Face, in 2023, which debuted at number one in South Korea and Japan and number two on the US Billboard 200, making him the highest-charting Korean solo artist on the latter chart. The album's single \"Like Crazy\" became the first song by a Korean solo artist to debut at number one on the US Billboard Hot 100 in history. Jimin also became the first Korean solo artist to top the Billboard Artist 100 chart. In 2024, he released his second album, Muse, and its lead single \"Who\", which debuted at number one on the Billboard Global 200.\n\nIn 2018, he was awarded the fifth-class Hwagwan Order of Cultural Merit by the President of South Korea, along with the other members of BTS, for his contributions to Korean culture.","name":"Jimin","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"지민","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"ID","iso_639_1":"id","name":"Bahasa indonesia","english_name":"Indonesian","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"BR","iso_639_1":"pt","name":"Português","english_name":"Portuguese","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"朴智旻（박지민，Park Ji-min），藝名為Jimin（지민）。韓國歌手，男子團體防彈少年團的成員，為最後一位入選的成員，在團內擔任主舞及領唱。2013年6月13日，透過單曲專輯《2 COOL 4 SKOOL》韓國出道。2014年6月4日，透過日語單曲《NO MORE DREAM -Japanese Ver.-》在日本出道。2023年3月24日，推出首張solo專輯《FACE》。","name":"朴智旻","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"JIMIN","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"樸智旻（박지민，Park Ji - min），藝名為 Jimin（지민）。韓國歌手，男子團體防彈少年團的成員，為最後一位入選的成員，在團內擔任主舞及領唱。2013 年 6 月 13 日，透過單曲專輯《2 COOL 4 SKOOL》韓國出道。2014 年 6 月 4 日，透過日語單曲《NO MORE DREAM -Japanese Ver. -》在日本出道。2023 年 3 月 24 日，推出首張 solo 專輯《FACE》。","name":"樸智旻","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}}]}}}}